Nonye is an AI performance coach who designs ambient user interfaces using pen, paper and AI to build meaningful connections with her SWE audience. 

She leverages sentiment analysis to uncover monetizable patterns in SWE mindshare, establishing the groundwork for multimodal AI in peer-to-peer advertising. 
Her research focuses on applying reinforcement learning techniques to resolve cognitive resource allocation challenges to enable seamless connection and disconnection cycles during testing of always-on AI.
